WEBVTT

00:02.505 --> 00:04.424
Previously on "The Path"...

00:04.424 --> 00:07.263
We need to purge this movement
of darkness, of Steve.

00:07.263 --> 00:09.852
‐ How?
‐ We tell everyone.

00:09.852 --> 00:11.689
‐ The end is gonna be in Bali.

00:11.689 --> 00:13.943
‐ Who told you about Bali?
‐ I saw it.

00:13.943 --> 00:16.658
‐ What if you came
to work for me?

00:16.658 --> 00:18.410
I want you on the team
when I run for Governor.

00:18.410 --> 00:20.081
‐ I'm getting you out of here.
Come on.

00:20.081 --> 00:21.458
‐ Look, I‐I can't.

00:21.458 --> 00:22.795
‐ What is wrong with you?
‐ Don't‐‐

00:25.049 --> 00:27.721
‐ We have to cut off ties
and end the trip to Bali.

00:27.721 --> 00:30.309
‐ You won't get better
unless you leave this place.

00:30.309 --> 00:33.107
If you don't get better,
I can't love you.

00:33.107 --> 00:37.448
‐ Eddie, I believe in you.
I believe in this movement.

00:37.448 --> 00:38.827
I would destroy everything

00:38.827 --> 00:41.248
I worked so fucking hard
to put behind me!

00:41.248 --> 00:43.503
‐ Steve needs to be
written out of Revelation.

00:43.503 --> 00:45.256
‐ The Movement won't survive.

00:45.256 --> 00:47.636
‐ They are not here for Steve.
They are here for me.

00:47.636 --> 00:50.474
‐ No, I can't let you do that.
I won't let you do that.

